{"tid":31392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"佛界清泉 猿虧法師 首創親子DIY舍利子工作坊","createTime":"2016-12-09T15:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T16:04:46.000Z","uid":31691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a50fbcc764d2aee5a5f9055e401faf242638832","tid":31392,"uid":31691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"==========親子DIY舍利子工作坊==========<br />\n<br />\n舍利子，意為屍體或身骨，通常指遺體火化後得到的殘餘骨燼，形狀有圓形、橢圓形、蓮花形，顏色也不同，有白、黑、綠、紅等。想睇下自己既舍利子係點樣樣？有機會啦！猿虧法師將會主持「親子DIY舍利子工作坊」，到時歡迎各位3-12歲既小朋友帶埋爸爸媽媽一齊燒左自己，製作屬於自己既舍利子！費用全免！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/09/235627_3a2b2c3895f843bfa9838ecedc4620e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2F235627_3a2b2c3895f843bfa9838ecedc4620e5.jpg&h=b6ee2a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇教友想一齊參加？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d788cd91e81a5ca5aa5b09fc73800d50f4cb6ed","tid":31392,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"燒咗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afc97c0058757af7f79fe4a5026cd10c3315bb5","tid":31392,"uid":31691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒咗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然香港已經冇得救<br />\n我諗燒左自己係一個出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}